You need python3 and pip3 for this

To install run:
python3 setup.py install

With optional flags:
--user                  :  Install in PYTHONUSERBASE directory (default $HOME/.local)
                        :  Recomended to run :
                        :  $ PYTHONUSERBASE=${MYDESTINATION} python3 setup.py install --user
--install_reqs          :  Installing requirements
--pipoptions  "OPTIONS" :  Extra options for pip3
--verbose               :  Verbose installation